pull.title: [Qt][RPC] Autocomplete commands for 'help' command in debug console
pull.body: Puts the commands in the autocompletion box when doing a `help <command>` command in the debug console.

events.message:
'help' rpc commands autocomplete

Adds autocompletion of the commands for when getting the help of a command by using `help <command>`

events.body: Nice. Concept ACK. Will test soon.
